Sales Leadfor Asian market (mainly for Japan or Korea)

Branford Limited is currently looking for a talented and motivated Sales Lead with excellent knowledge of Asian Toy markets (mainly Japanese and Korean) to develop the sales of our brands in these markets. Please check all of the brands on www.Battatco.com

Responsibilities:

Provide administrative support to sales in connection with processing of inquiries, sales planning and sales orders for retailers in Asian Market.
Work closely with Digital Marketing team to provide data insights & ad hoc analyses of Asian market trends;
Prepare and submit for approval, item presentations, quote sheets on customer specific format and requirements;
Represent the company at marketing events such as trade shows;
Assist in general office work and other administrative tasks as required. 

Skills, Competencies & Requirements: 

Knowledge of Japanese/ Korean culture
Japanese / Korean with Excellent knowledge of English to deal with foreign divisions and Japanese / Korean customers is an advantage
Strong knowledge and experience using Microsoft Office including Outlook & Excel;
Ability to work as a team;
Exceptional organizational, administrative skills and attention to detail;
Strong sense of responsibility;
Able to multitask effectively and manage priorities;
Ability to adapt to a constantly changing and dynamic environment;
Some travel required (10%);
A university degree in a related field

Experience: 

Minimum 5 years of experience in toy industry  

